creator: Mary Roberts Rinehart and Irvin S. Cobb
description:
LibriVox recording of Oh, Well, You Know How Women Are and Isn't That Just Like a Man! by Mary Roberts Rinehart and Irvin S. Cobb.

Read in English by David Wales; MaryAnn

This warm, affectionate duet of essays by two of the early twentieth century's most popular writers is a bit dated but still entertaining. Summary by David Wales.

For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

M4B Format Available
